## AT65C02 Adaptations - MIT License

**Author:** kayto@github.com  
**Year:** 2025

### Modifications for AT65C02 System

- Updated hardcoded VIA and ACIA memory locations for AT65C02 hardware
- Modified memory map configurations (cfgs) for AT65C02 default layout
- Integration with SMON monitor and shell system
- Loadable module implementation for AT65C02 architecture

### Build System

Uses Visual Studio Code with Docker-based cc65 toolchain:
- **Docker Image:** dbuchwald/cc65-tools
- **Source:** https://github.com/dbuchwald/cc65-tools
- **License:** Apache License 2.0
- Includes /common and .vscode directories from Dawid Buchwald

